  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: cb567088341fa3c4b9b5217e379ebde5, type: 3}
  m_Name: ExplorerStartMeet
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialogueText
  speakerName: Penjelah
  lines:
  - Oh, hello there. A Box Agent? In this day and age?
  - 'A rare sight for sure, I wonder if I may encounter others? '
  - Ah, of course, where are my manners? My name is Penjelah, I am an explorer.
  - Well, I will now be, anyways. My brother, Tokang, runs that small shop just next
    to us.
  - Business hasn't been great, possibly due to our current location.
  - Moving away is risky, however. These lands are no walk in the park.
  - I will be going explore to find supplies so we can survive.
  - I assume you're doing the same, even if for different reasons.
  - I wish you the best of luck, friend. May I see you somewhere out in this vast
    world.
